      News story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Portland Scrap Metal fined for keeping waste vehicles
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The Dorset firm disputed the vehicles were end-of-life when they entered the site but admitted breaching the enforcement notice after ignoring several warnings.</p>

  </div>
</div>

